window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>There's a masked killer on the loose, and he's obsessed with one thingâ€”breaking her.</b></p> <p>Seraphina Valez has lived through harrowing times, but nothing could have prepared her for Orion Adair. Not his looks. Or his charm. And certainly not the vicious beast lurking beneath his skin.</p> <p>But Seraphina has a backbone, and she'll need it to protect her heart from her scarred and tattooed kidnapper. Especially when being bound and at his mercy starts to seem like a good thing...</p> <p>Orion Adair has never wanted anything more than Seraphina. Not even getting out of prison for a lifetime sentence.</p> <p>Putting on a plague mask and chasing her through the woods isn't enough to win this woman's heart. He's going to have to change his ways and step into the role of protector. Especially when the mysterious organization she's been hiding from for ten years comes to collect her.</p> <p>Little do they know, Seraphina already belongs to him. Anyone who touches her will pay the ultimate price.</p> <p><i>Contains mature content. A complete list of content warnings can be found on the author's website.</i></p>"; 
